{"tid":2295754,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一個食住你上既女仔","createTime":"2020-11-22T04:23:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-22T10:25:55.000Z","uid":371674,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1708ead9030c7982fcf82717218facea3176369a","tid":2295754,"uid":371674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T04:23:17.000Z","msg":"我自己係打機到識左個女仔<br />\n佢細我好多 反而仲臭串過我<br />\n好多野我都係比佢屌得多<br />\n我其實對佢有啲好感既<br />\n但自從星期五之後 <br />\n我Post左張同女仔食飯既相<br />\n佢即刻好似唔太想理我<br />\n對我不理不采咁 一句起兩句止<br />\n平時會聊下我打機 串下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n女仔真係好介意男仔同其他人出街?<br />\n我極度懷疑佢嬲左我 但我無證據<br />\n有無人可以幫下我 點樣氹返佢<br />\nSorry for 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d642b4626e7bcfbf973b18089cd104b87192bd7","tid":2295754,"uid":201604,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T04:24:07.000Z","msg":"你已做兵"},{"pid":"1835d27258a6fe21a4efc6a27b922cf849fa8d3f","tid":2295754,"uid":371674,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d642b4626e7bcfbf973b18089cd104b87192bd7","tid":2295754,"uid":201604,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T04:24:07.000Z","msg":"你已做兵"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T04:26:22.000Z","msg":"做兵也有做兵既樂趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n兵都會享受追佢既快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樣衰既我唯有咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"537061930dee02507ac852ef712aa5e87f8c81f5","tid":2295754,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1835d27258a6fe21a4efc6a27b922cf849fa8d3f","tid":2295754,"uid":371674